\c 6
\p
\v 1 Wakaendepi mudiwa wako, iwe wakanaka pakati pevakadzi? Wakatendeukirepi, kuti timutsvake pamwe newe?
\v 2 Mudiwa wangu wakaburukira kubindu rake, kundima dzezvinonhuhwira, kunodya mumapindu, nekuunganidza maruva.
\v 3 Ini ndiri womudiwa wangu; mudiwa wangu ndowangu; anofudza makwai ake pakati pamaruva.
\s Chikomba nemwenga vanorumbidzana
\p
\v 4 Wakanaka, shamwari yangu saTiriza, wakanaka seJerusarema, unotyisa sehondo ine mireza.
\v 5 Usanditarira nameso ako, nokuti andikunda. Vhudzi rako rakafanana neboka rembudzi, dzinoburukira mujinga megomo reGiriyadhi.
\v 6 Meno aka akafanana neboka renhunzvi dzamakwai, dzinobva pakushambwa; rimwe nerimwe radzo rina vana vaviri, hakuna rimwe risina mwana.
\v 7 Zvavovo zvako zvakafanana nebhande repomegiranati pakutarira kwako pakati pechifukidzo chako.
\v 8 Vahosi vana makumi matanhatu navarongo vana makumi masere variko, nemhandara dzisingaperi.
\v 9 Njiva yangu, akakwana wangu, ndiye umwe ega; ndiye mwana umwe wega wamai vake; ndiye musanangurwa wowakamubereka; vakunda vakamuona, vakati akaropafadzwa; navahosi navarongo, vakamurumbidza.
\p
\v 10 Ndianiko uyo anotarira samambakwedza, akanaka somwedzi, akachena sezuva, anotyisa sehondo ine mireza?
\p
\v 11 Ndakaburukira kumunda wenzungu, kuti ndione miti mitema mumupata, kuti ndione kana muzambiringa wotunga, kana mapomegiranati otunga maruva.
\v 12 Ndisati ndazviziva, mweya wangu wakandigadza pangoro dzoumambo dzavanhu vangu.
\p
\v 13 Dzoka, dzoka, Shuramiti; dzoka, dzoka, kuti tikutarire. Munoda kutarira muShuramiti neiko, sezvamunotarira kutamba kwendaza mbiri?
